Validation / Acceptance Criteria:
- Default value check: IF ((read_reg(addr_array[i]) & 0xFFFFFFFE) == default_value_array[i]) PASS; ELSE { def_fail_cnt++ }
- Write/read check: For writable+readable and non-skipped registers, IF ((read_reg(addr) & read_mask_array[i]) == exp_val) PASS; ELSE { wr_fail_cnt++ }
- Overall: IF (def_fail_cnt == 0 && wr_fail_cnt == 0) finish(0) => PASS; ELSE finish(1) => FAIL.
